# 💰 Funding & Legal

## Legal Structure (Recommended)

Two entities, one mission:

### Rastrum A.C. (Asociación Civil)
- Holds mission, trademark, grants, community, data-governance rules
- 3–8 weeks to incorporate · MXN 15–40K notario fees
- Pursue **donataria autorizada** (SAT, 12 months) → enables FMCN, FAHHO, Fomento Banamex grants
- Model: Mozilla Foundation, WordPress.org Foundation, iNaturalist 501(c)(3)

### Rastrum S.A.S. (same-day via tuempresa.gob.mx, ~MXN 0)
- Commercial licensing, SaaS contracts, government B2G, eventual VC equity
- A.C. owns 100% initially; trademark + services agreement between entities
- B Corp certification via SAPI (Sistema B doesn't certify nonprofits)

### U.S. 501(c)(3) Fiscal Sponsor
Needed to unlock AWS Imagine, Bezos Earth Fund, CZI EOSS, Mulago, DRK, and most U.S.-origin philanthropy:
- **Multiplier** (conservation-specialized, 9% fee) — recommended
- Social Good Fund (faster, ~5 days, but 1000:100 ratio)

