## License Stack

| Code | License | Rationale |
|------|---------|-----------|
| Server code | **AGPL-3.0** | Closes SaaS loophole (Mastodon/Nextcloud precedent) |
| Client SDKs | **Apache 2.0** | Adds patent grant |
| Documentation | **CC BY 4.0** | Open sharing |
| Taxonomic tables | **CC0** | Public domain |
| Indigenous glossaries | **TK Labels + community license** | CARE > FAIR |
| Small ML models | **Apache 2.0** | |
| Frontier models | **Rastrum Research License** | Free non-commercial, commercial requires agreement |

**DCO (Developer Certificate of Origin)** not CLA — lightweight, trust-friendly.

