## Trademark

File immediately at IMPI in class 42 (SaaS) + class 9 (software) + class 41 (education).
~MXN 3,126/class + MXN 5–15K attorney fees · 6–18 months to issuance.

⚠️ **Inventia Life Science (Sydney) has a RASTRUM™ 3D bioprinter** — confirm via [MARCANET](https://marcanet.impi.gob.mx/) before filing.

Register domains: `rastrum.mx` · `rastrum.org.mx` · `rastrum.app` · `rastrum.ai` · `rastrum.eco`

